---
import Breadcrumbs from '../components/Breadcrumbs.astro';
import PageHeader from '../components/PageHeader.astro';
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Accessibility statement"
  description="Accessibility statement for Marie Harding Counselling Service website."
  canonicalPath="/accessibility-statement"
>
  <div class="space-y-6">
    <Breadcrumbs items={[{ label: 'Home', href: '/' }, { label: 'Accessibility statement' }]} />
    <PageHeader
      title="Accessibility statement"
      intro="Marie Harding Counselling Service is committed to making this website usable for as many people as possible."
    />
  </div>

  <article class="prose-safe mt-8">
    <h2>Accessibility standards</h2>
    <p>
      This website aims to meet core WCAG 2.2 AA requirements, including semantic structure,
      keyboard navigation, focus visibility, readable text, and high contrast.
    </p>

    <h2>Features in place</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Skip link to main content.</li>
      <li>Keyboard-focus styles on interactive elements.</li>
      <li>Responsive mobile-first layout.</li>
      <li>Labelled form fields and clear messaging.</li>
      <li>Reduced motion support and print-friendly styles.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Known limitations</h2>
    <p>
      Some third-party embeds, such as map content, may have accessibility limitations outside this website's direct control.
    </p>

    <h2>Feedback and support</h2>
    <p>
      If you experience any accessibility issue, please make contact and details can be addressed as quickly as possible.
    </p>

    <p><strong>Last reviewed:</strong> 5 March 2026.</p>
  </article>
</Layout>
